<i>noun</i>: 형평성 [형평썽], 평탄 [평탄], 일률 [일률] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>형평성 [형평썽]</dt><br>
<dd>fairness; equity; evenness</dd><br>
<dd>어느 한쪽으로 기울거나 치우치지 않고 균형을 이루는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of keeping balance without leaning or tilting to one side.</dd><br>
<dt>평탄 [평탄]</dt><br>
<dd>1. evenness; flatness</dd><br>
<dd>바닥이 고르고 넓음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a floor being even and spacious.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calmness; peace of mind</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 편하고 조용함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's mind being comfortable and quiet.</dd><br>
<dd>3. smoothness; favorableness</dd><br>
<dd>일이 미리 생각한 대로 잘되어 나감.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a project, etc., being in smooth progress, as planned.</dd><br>
<dt>일률 [일률]</dt><br>
<dd>uniformity; evenness</dd><br>
<dd>일을 처리하는 태도나 방식이 한결같음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a way or mindset of dealing with a certain work is uniform.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>